{"tid":1451381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你地老母 當手足係condom呀?","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:21:29.000Z","uid":112197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b26178741f3172290f812227d9beea0638715f92","tid":1451381,"uid":112197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:55:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_qB251XKrdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_qB251XKrdA&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=75bc837e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_qB251XKrdA</a><br />\n睇到我好撚嬲 三四個人行到面前 <br />\n見到比人打到趴係到既手足竟然運路走<br />\n<br />\n難以想像手足有幾無助 自已比人擒住 <br />\n成百人係身邊走緊 冇人望到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行到面前運路走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得一位義士肯出手 但冇用 最後都係被擒<br />\n會比人告暴動 分分鐘坐十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道當時有鬼趕人走<br />\n有人叫&quot;走啦 仲另轉頭望&quot;<br />\n但大家可唔可以唔好咁淆?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要企硬 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">冷静啲望住前面向後慢慢退</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解對陣會比人拉? 唔係你地走得唔夠快<br />\n係你地連背後有咩都唔望 另轉身瘋狂跑<br />\n<br />\n戰場上 面對炮火前進既士兵比 撤退時背對敵人既士兵更容易生存<br />\n前者有後方友軍炮火支援 後者背脊係任人魚肉<br />\n<br />\n你地對唔對得住<br />\n跑唔快 跌親既 殿後 攞住物資既義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你淆一淆 佢地坐十年<br />\n說好的齊上齊落? 為救人出黎既手足呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係為分化而黎<br />\n我應承大家會殿後 會做最尾頂住班仆街嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地應承我 手足被狗擒 可唔可以真係去救佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5306f92cbe9459951b431c85ccb52ed9f95fc6","tid":1451381,"uid":112197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:21:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}